<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Job Alert</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h2 style="color: #c0392b;">Job Alert: {{statusLabel}}</h2>

  <p>Er is een job met status <strong>{{statusLabel}}</strong> gedetecteerd in het systeem.</p>

  <h3 style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px;">Job Details</h3>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold; width: 140px;">Job URI:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><a href="{{jobUri}}">{{jobUri}}</a></td>
    </tr>
    {{#if jobUuid}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Job UUID:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{jobUuid}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Status:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><a href="{{status}}">{{statusLabel}}</a></td>
    </tr>
    {{#if operation}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Operation:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><a href="{{operation}}">{{operationLabel}}</a></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if created}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Aangemaakt:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{created}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if modified}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Laatst gewijzigd:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;">{{modified}}</td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
    {{#if creator}}
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;">Creator:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><a href="{{creator}}">{{creator}}</a></td>
    </tr>
    {{/if}}
  </table>

  {{#if tasks.length}}
  <h3 style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 20px;">Taken</h3>
  {{#each tasks}}
  <div style="background-color: {{#if (eq this.statusLabel 'failed')}}#fdecea{{else}}#f9f9f9{{/if}}; border-left: 4px solid {{#if (eq this.statusLabel 'failed')}}#c0392b{{else}}#ddd{{/if}}; padding: 10px 15px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0;"><strong>Task {{this.index}}:</strong> {{this.operationLabel}}</p>
    <p style="margin: 0 0 5px 0; font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">Status: <strong>{{this.statusLabel}}</strong></p>
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.85em; color: #888;">URI: <a href="{{this.uri}}">{{this.uri}}</a></p>
    {{#if this.error}}
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; padding: 10px; background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #e74c3c; color: #c0392b;">
      <strong>Error:</strong> {{this.error}}
    </p>
    {{/if}}
  </div>
  {{/each}}
  {{/if}}

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 30px 0 20px 0;">

  <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
    Als dit probleem aanhoudt, neem dan contact op met het ontwikkelteam.
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;">
    Met vriendelijke groeten,<br>
    <strong>Het LBLOD development team</strong>
  </p>

  <p style="font-size: 0.8em; color: #999; margin-top: 30px;">
    Opgelet, reageren op deze mail kan niet. Voor verdere hulp, mail naar <a
        style="color: #007bff; text-decoration: none" href="mailto:loketlokaalbestuur@vlaanderen.be" target="_blank">loketlokaalbestuur@vlaanderen.be</a>.
  </p>
</body>
</html>
